<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.2.2">
<l>vaitta neyyuṅ kāynta pālum vaṭita yirum naṟuveṇ ṇeyu</l>
<l>mitta ṉaiyum peṟra ṟiyē ṉempi rāṉnī piṟanta piṉṉai</l>
<l>yetta ṉaiyuñ ceyyap peṟṟā yētuñ ceyyēṉ katampa ṭātē</l>
<l>mutta ṉaiya muṟuval ceytu mūkku ṟiñci mulaiyu ṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>After your birth, my Lord, obtaining even this much stored ghee,</l>
<l>heated milk, strained curds, or fragrant butter, I do not know.</l>
<l>You get to do whatever [you want], I do nothing.</l>
<l>[Please], without being angry, showing [your] pearl-like teeth</l>
<l>and sniffling with [your] nose, drink [from my] breast!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
